      • getEndpointURIs

        public Collection<String> getEndpointURIs(String includePattern)
        Description copied from interface: EndpointRegistry
        Gets endpoint URIs which match specified pattern.

        Example: method with the following pattern ^(spring-ws|servlet).*$ will return URIs which starts by spring-ws or servlet.

        Specified by:
        getEndpointURIs in interface EndpointRegistry
        Parameters:
        includePattern - pattern for filtering endpoints URI - only whose URIs will match specified pattern will be returned
        Returns:
        collection of endpoint URIs
